      • makeExchange

        public void makeExchange(ResourceList offerer,
                ResourceList receiver)
                  throws TradeException
        Makes this trade between two ResourceLists
        Parameters:
        offerer - the ResourceList to trade from
        receiver - the ResourceList to trade to
        Throws:
        TradeException - if either of the preconditions are not met
        Preconditions
        • The offerer has at least what is offered
        • the receiver has at least what is wanted.
        Postconditions
        The offered resources will be taken from the offerer and given to the receiver and the wanted resources will be taken from the receiver and given to the offerer.
